## Check for non-linearity

# quadratic term for vax

astra_mod1 = lm(willingness~vax +
                  I(vax^2)+
                  age*frame, data = astra)

partial_residual_plot(willingness~age, 
                      model=astra_mod1, 
                      added_term = ~age, 
                      data=astra) + 
  xlab("Age") + 
  theme_bw()

partial_residual_plot(willingness~age | frame, 
                      model=astra_mod1, 
                      added_term = ~age*frame, 
                      data=astra) + 
  xlab("Age") + 
  theme_bw()

### Plot vax

partial_residual_plot(willingness~vax, 
                      model=astra_mod1, 
                      added_term = ~vax + I(vax^2), 
                      data=astra) +
  xlab("Vaccination Hesitency")+
  theme_bw()

astra_mod2 = lm(willingness~vax + I(vax^2) +
